about.text: MapViewer is the top-of-the-line app to work with maps uploaded in XML-format. The application runs on most desktop browsers (ex. Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge, Opera, e.t.c.) and mobile phones.
feedback: If you have any questions or problems, please, report them at leins275@gmail.com
helpOnChoosing: Choose the types of data you want to see.
